title: OK-410
content:
OK410 是款双高音、双中音、单10寸全频高档KTV包房音箱，采用高密度板喷黑色环保漆箱体，设有标准的安装吊挂点，选择优质单元，使音箱音色格外亮丽突出，中频宽厚，高频细腻恬美，低频深沉动力十足！箱体两边设计有井字型装饰曹！
  OK410 is a double high、double middle、single 10 inch all frequency high-grade KTV rooms sound box, use high-density plate spray black paint box, equipped with standard installation hanging point, choose high quality unit, the speakers sound exceptionally bright highlight, intermediate frequency generous, high-frequency exquisite pleasantness, low-frequency deep motivation! On both sides of the box body design has well type decoration cao!
阻抗Impedance：8  Ohm
额定功率Long-term power（rms）：200W
峰值功率Peak Power Handling：400W
频响Frequency response：50-20KHZ
灵敏度Sensitivity：92dB
低频Low：10INx1
中频Mid：3 INx2
高频High：3 INx2
重量N.W：15KG
箱体尺寸：501x291x286mm
